publisher			Vonsnake							
publish_time	 2016年5月30日		
desc_long								关于这款游戏							BallisticNG is a free anti-gravity racing game. You can play as a variety of teams competing in the 2159 Anti-Gravity League, each with their own unique vehicles. Visually the game emulates the limitations of the Playstation One hardware and a lot of care has been made into making sure it looks authentic while including more modern graphic techniques. The game has 5 different speed classes for different skill sets, starting off slow and eventually becoming brutally fast.Features14 tracks in different locations13 teams setup for different play styles5 gamemodes - Arcade, Time Trial, Free Play, Tournament and SurvivalA variety of weapons for damaging and slowing other racersModding Tools - Track Editor, Ship Editor and Custom SoundsCockpit view - each ship has a unique cockpit!A soundtrack full of songs inspired by electronic music from the 90s Early Access As an early access notice, the dev team are very happy to help out in the game's community discussions if you have any issues with the game at all. We check it often so you should get a response fairly quickly and if the problem is big enough, you can expect a fix in the next update. As part of Early Access, BallisticNG is getting very frequent updates, sometimes small and sometimes big.Welcome to BallisticNG. Buckle up, pilots.						
